channel.description: YouTube Video Resources Slides Video Script Hello, and welcome to the week seven Announcements video for CC 515 in spring 2023. So this month really, you should have gotten milestone three done late last week. So hopefully you’ve got that done and turned in, I’ll be grading those soon. And then for the rest of the month of March, you’ll basically be working on the week four and week five lessons, where we’re going to pivot a lot into building our own back end servers and building more Database Driven websites.
